This a NLP project am using NLTK for this project this project is used to summarize the review 
so when theres a huge review instead of reading that whole this just copy past the review in the webpage
and then you get summarized review.
I have created a basic frontend using HTML,CSS in this.
Commands to run the code:-
check python version incase u dont have download it 
>>pip install -r requirements.text
>>python
>>import nltk
nltk.download("punkt")
nltk.download("stopwords")
>>exit()
>>python app.py

